\framet{Homomorphisms}{

A \emph{functor} |F| maps arrows from one category to another, preserving |Category| structure:
\begin{code}
F id == id

F (g . f) == F g . F f
\end{code}

\ 

\pause
A \emph{cartesian functor} |F| additionally preserves |cartesian| structure:
\begin{code}
F exl  == exl

F exr  == exr

F (f &&& g)  == F f &&& F g
\end{code}
}
