\framel{Compositional matrices}{
Sufficient to build arbitrary ``matrices'':
\vspace{3ex}
\begin{code}
  scale  :: a -> (a `k` a)                              -- $1\times1$

  (|||)  :: (a `k` c) -> (b `k` c) -> ((a :* b) `k` c)  -- horizontal juxt

