\begin{itemize}\itemsep2.5ex
\item Simple AD algorithm, specializing to forward, reverse, mixed.
\item No graphs, tapes, tags, partial derivatives, or mutation.
\item Parallel-friendly and low memory use.
\item Calculated
  % rigorously
  from simple, regular
  algebra problems.
